postcontent: This is an excellent condition ArmaLite M4C carbine in 5.56mm. It is an early ArmaLite made during the 1994/2004 AWB. I believe the "C" in the M4C model designation stands for compliant. As you can see there is no bayonet lug, an A2 full length stock and a compensator instead of a flash suppressor at the muzzle. The carbine has a really nice feel to it, swings easily and mounts to your shoulder very comfortably due to the A2 buttstock. The carbine is lightly used and in truly great condition even though it is probably at least 10 years old. I've shot approx 100 rounds through it and it is very accurate. The carbine will be shipped in a hard case with one 30 round magazine.
